{"id":127,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":127,"title":"D&C 123","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 123"],[".studyIntro",["i","Duty of the Saints in relation to their persecutors, as written by Joseph Smith the Prophet while a prisoner in the jail at Liberty, Missouri. This section is an excerpt from an epistle to the Church dated March 20, 1839 (see the",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.head"},"heading to section 121"],")."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.1-6"},"1–6"],", The Saints should collect and publish an account of their sufferings and persecutions;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.7-10"},"7–10"],", The same spirit that established the false creeds also leads to persecution of the Saints;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.11-17"},"11–17"],", Many among all sects will yet receive the truth."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.1","order":"06.05.123.15234"},["b","1"],"And again, we would suggest for your consideration the propriety of all the saints",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"gathering"],"up a knowledge of all the facts, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"sufferings"],"and abuses put upon them by the people of this State;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.2","order":"06.05.123.15235"},["b","2"],"And also of all the property and amount of damages which they have sustained, both of character and personal",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"injuries"],", as well as real property;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.3","order":"06.05.123.15236"},["b","3"],"And also the names of all persons that have had a hand in their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"oppressions"],", as far as they can get hold of them and find them out."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.4","order":"06.05.123.15237"},["b","4"],"And perhaps a committee can be appointed to find out these things, and to take",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"statements"],"and affidavits; and also to gather up the libelous publications that are afloat;"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.5","order":"06.05.123.15238"},["b","5"],"And all that are in the magazines, and in the encyclopedias, and all the libelous histories that are published, and are writing, and by whom, and present the whole concatenation of diabolical rascality and nefarious and murderous impositions that have been practiced upon this people—"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.6","order":"06.05.123.15239"},["b","6"],"That we may not only publish to all the world, but present them to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"heads"],"of government in all their dark and hellish hue, as the last effort which is enjoined on us by our Heavenly Father, before we can fully and completely claim that promise which shall call him forth from his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"hiding place"],"; and also that the whole nation may be left without excuse before he can send forth the power of his mighty arm."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.7","order":"06.05.123.15240"},["b","7"],"It is an imperative duty that we owe to God, to angels, with whom we shall be brought to stand, and also to ourselves, to our wives and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"children"],", who have been made to bow down with grief, sorrow, and care, under the most damning hand of murder, tyranny, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"oppression"],", supported and urged on and upheld by the influence of that spirit which hath so strongly riveted the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"creeds"],"of the fathers, who have inherited lies, upon the hearts of the children, and filled the world with confusion, and has been growing stronger and stronger, and is now the very mainspring of all corruption, and the whole",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_7d"},"earth"],"groans under the weight of its iniquity."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.8","order":"06.05.123.15241"},["b","8"],"It is an iron",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"yoke"],", it is a strong band; they are the very handcuffs, and chains, and shackles, and fetters of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"hell"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.9","order":"06.05.123.15242"},["b","9"],"Therefore it is an imperative duty that we owe, not only to our own wives and children, but to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"widows"],"and fatherless, whose husbands and fathers have been",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"murdered"],"under its iron hand;"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.10","order":"06.05.123.15243"},["b","10"],"Which dark and blackening deeds are enough to make hell itself",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"shudder"],", and to stand aghast and pale, and the hands of the very devil to tremble and palsy."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.11","order":"06.05.123.15244"},["b","11"],"And also it is an imperative duty that we owe to all the rising generation, and to all the pure in heart—"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.12","order":"06.05.123.15245"},["b","12"],"For there are many yet on the earth among all sects, parties, and denominations, who are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"blinded"],"by the subtle",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"craftiness"],"of men, whereby they lie in wait to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"deceive"],", and who are only kept from the truth because they",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_12d"},"know not"],"where to find it—"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.13","order":"06.05.123.15246"},["b","13"],"Therefore, that we should waste and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"wear"],"out our lives in bringing to light all the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"hidden things"],"of darkness, wherein we know them; and they are truly manifest from heaven—"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.14","order":"06.05.123.15247"},["b","14"],"These should then be attended to with great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"earnestness"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.15","order":"06.05.123.15248"},["b","15"],"Let no man count them as small things; for there is much which lieth in futurity, pertaining to the saints, which depends upon these things."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.16","order":"06.05.123.15249"},["b","16"],"You know, brethren, that a very large ship is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"benefited"],"very much by a very small helm in the time of a storm, by being kept workways with the wind and the waves."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.17","order":"06.05.123.15250"},["b","17"],"Therefore, dearly beloved brethren, let us",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"cheerfully"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"do"],"all things that lie in our power; and then may we stand still, with the utmost assurance, to see the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"salvation"],"of God, and for his arm to be revealed."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.1a","order":"06.05.123.15251"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/69.8"},"D&C 69:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.1b","order":"06.05.123.15253"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/4.1.1-24"},"Ezra 4:1 (1–24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.2a","order":"06.05.123.15255"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/injustice"},"TG Injustice"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.3a","order":"06.05.123.15257"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/oppression"},"TG Oppression"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.4a","order":"06.05.123.15259"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/record-keeping"},"TG Record Keeping"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.6a","order":"06.05.123.15261"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/5.8.8-17"},"Ezra 5:8 (8–17)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.6b","order":"06.05.123.15263"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.89"},"D&C 101:89"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.4.1,4"},"121:4 (1, 4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.7a","order":"06.05.123.15265"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-children-responsibilities-toward"},"TG Family, Children, Responsibilities toward"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.7b","order":"06.05.123.15267"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cruelty"},"TG Cruelty"],"."],["div",{"id":"7c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.7c","order":"06.05.123.15269"},["b","7c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/24.7"},"Alma 24:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.19"},"JS—H 1:19"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/traditions-of-men"},"TG Traditions of Men"],"."],["div",{"id":"7d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.7d","order":"06.05.123.15271"},["b","7d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/33.9"},"Isa. 33:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/7.49"},"Moses 7:49"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.8a","order":"06.05.123.15273"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bondage-physical"},"TG Bondage, Physical"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bondage-spiritual"},"Bondage, Spiritual"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.8b","order":"06.05.123.15275"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hell"},"TG Hell"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.9a","order":"06.05.123.15277"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/children"},"TG Children"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/widows"},"Widows"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.9b","order":"06.05.123.15279"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/98.13"},"D&C 98:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/103.27.27-28"},"103:27 (27–28)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/124.54"},"124:54"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.10a","order":"06.05.123.15281"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/14.9.4-11"},"Isa. 14:9 (4–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.12a","order":"06.05.123.15283"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.8"},"Col. 2:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.75"},"D&C 76:75"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spiritual-blindness"},"TG Spiritual Blindness"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.12b","order":"06.05.123.15285"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-doctrine"},"TG False Doctrine"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-prophets"},"False Prophets"],"."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.12c","order":"06.05.123.15287"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/2.18.16-23"},"Col. 2:18 (16–23)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.12d","order":"06.05.123.15289"},["b","12d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/8.21.19-24"},"1 Ne. 8:21 (19–24)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mission-of-latter-day-saints"},"TG Mission of Latter-day Saints"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.13a","order":"06.05.123.15291"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/dedication"},"TG Dedication"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.13b","order":"06.05.123.15293"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/4.5"},"1 Cor. 4:5"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/secret-combinations"},"TG Secret Combinations"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.14a","order":"06.05.123.15295"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zeal"},"TG Zeal"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.16a","order":"06.05.123.15297"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/james/3.4"},"James 3:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/16.29"},"1 Ne. 16:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/37.6.6-8"},"Alma 37:6 (6–8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/64.33"},"D&C 64:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.17a","order":"06.05.123.15299"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cheerful"},"TG Cheerful"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.17b","order":"06.05.123.15301"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/initiative"},"TG Initiative"],"."],["div",{"id":"17c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/123.17c","order":"06.05.123.15303"},["b","17c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/14.13"},"Ex. 14:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/30.15"},"Isa. 30:15"],"."]]}
